{
  "stem": "9730.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And through the help of some relatives in, in this country, in Buffalo at the time, she got the necessary affidavits and, and was able to come here in '36.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as soon as she got here, she made it her business to prevail on, on some other relatives to send papers for me as well.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was successful in that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And also, this time slot happened to be a window during which it was still comparatively easy to get an American visa.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because this was the period before Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And so I, I was able to come in-- to the states in 1937.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my brother then followed me the next year in '38.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, of course.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, I remember, of course, the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] tremendously emotional farewell with my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It, it so happened that my father had decided to accompany me to Hamburg, from where I would take the ship that would take me to New York.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my, my brother also joined us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was not living in, in Waldorf.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was, of course, as I said, away in, in Breslau at the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he joined us, also came to Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I, I remember, of course, the feelings I had.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we left on the note that, of course, we, the younger people, would establish ourselves in this country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we would see to it that our parents would also come.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I had a chest of some of my belongings, a lot, a lot of books, some clothes, and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a few mementos of my parents' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] home, and a, a, a few silver spoons, things like that.",
      "word_count": 44
    }
  ],
